## My Solution

```sql
SELECT
  ROUND(COUNT(*) FILTER(WHERE signup_action = 'Confirmed')*1.0 / COUNT(*), 2) AS confirm_rate
FROM emails e
left JOIN texts t ON t.email_id = e.email_id AND t.signup_action = 'Confirmed'
```

